# Backend API kök adresi (Zn.ClientWebApi). launchSettings.json'daki HTTP profili:
# http://localhost:5241 (https profili ayrica https://localhost:7253 sunar).
# Development'ta self-signed HTTPS sertifika dogrulama sorunlarindan kacinmak icin
# HTTP portu varsayilan alindi. HTTPS kullanmak isterseniz su satiri kullanin:
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://localhost:7253
VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:5241
